data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home is very well maintained with a list of upgrades. Seller has updated flooring throughout with vinyl plank floors in the living, kitchen, dining and hallways along with new carpet in bedrooms. Both showers have also had a make-over with new tile surround. The living room is accented with a statement, brick fireplace, and beautiful wainscoting. Plenty of storage throughout with extra linen closets, walk in bedroom closets, and an oversized laundry room. Sit outside and enjoy your patio and backyard with large trees that offer ample shade in spring and summer. This home is conveniently located one block from the community pool, clubhouse, splash pad, and park.
